{"tid":1456820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下收工嘅你地入機場","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:30:29.000Z","uid":93485,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3730d3c8c1a836a56d76f539b93765d360285e5","tid":1456820,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"求下你地翻轉頭 如果有義士今晚比人拉 <br />\n係散水狗有份助攻啊！<br />\n團結啲好無？？？？<br />\n求下你地 一齊入機場先係救人嘅方法"},{"pid":"d8cea779896048a9a61d5206e58b0b7b912aa094","tid":1456820,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"屌。俾2散水撚搞到好灰好慶"},{"pid":"8edd9561d5cf3024754ebc93aa4481231eeaa762","tid":1456820,"uid":35995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"Cls, 經過左咁多野，質素都係咁"},{"pid":"b280b56a08e4597031a39b45fd3f277aa010b0f2","tid":1456820,"uid":93485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"啲機而家開始有得登機！"},{"pid":"f9b7d0d412b66db9c96ee723473d3effca02509f","tid":1456820,"uid":271617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"By：黃之峰 facebook 現場 18:17<br />\n<br />\n目前我人仍在機埸，明白大家對於近日的抗議有一定憂慮，但實在無需過分恐慌，一些假消息傳出去也是不必要的。<br />\n<br />\n一、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#香港機場沒有切斷任何網絡</span></span>，順粹是人群聚集後網絡收得很差而已，過去遊行人數多的時候也有同樣狀況。<br />\n<br />\n二、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前機場燈火通明</span></span>，機場快綫及機場巴士仍正常運作，有推着行李的香港人仍然繼續前往機場，亦有示威者正在陸續離開，包括沿機場路步行至東涌。<br />\n<br />\n三、客運大樓的大部份商店已落閘，現場所見<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仍有過千名示威者</span></span>於接機大堂。<br />\n<br />\n四、目前<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仍有班機等待抵港</span></span>，包括夜晚8:30的班機，亦有班機等待飛離香港。"},{"pid":"2f0f7250da97aa279ae0b1db66d6f3390f4ec118","tid":1456820,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"求下你地翻轉頭 如果有義士今晚比人拉 係散水狗有份助攻啊！"},{"pid":"6fa0f17570cbd9583c503ad6e5f804e7ed754003","tid":1456820,"uid":93485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"求你地入翻機場"},{"pid":"91f91dd69a12dc4632dd8ba524fe89347e5c8361","tid":1456820,"uid":3431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"ok 有份叫散 轉頭一定再入 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bf601f66d93d222962e54c45e85bf5850cbfc8","tid":1456820,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e803aa173328120955e5c88a406a8d4c698db4","tid":1456820,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116d14c0584cc1604b92dc74e26bad2da1f6b7e3","tid":1456820,"uid":64957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b280b56a08e4597031a39b45fd3f277aa010b0f2","tid":1456820,"uid":93485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"啲機而家開始有得登機！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"其實啲客入咗禁區點都會登機<br />\nCX都有叫啲crew上機先<br />\n 而家今晚到2點嘅機已經停咗<br />\n雖然冇真係完全癱瘓機場<br />\n但如果佢地嚟多次64 2.0而我冇叫人走 <br />\n我諗我會後悔死"},{"pid":"ad21abf46ebc1dda7a95dc326cbfc5c5185bcf78","tid":1456820,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"有, 現在入"},{"pid":"09d4dad6023ef15cccebec7182de208b06c2251e","tid":1456820,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e770219499ca9a4c1cfe948f68417368c8f498","tid":1456820,"uid":289237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkg